					<outline text="British, U.S. experts arrive to help in Nigeria">
						<outline text="Link to Article" type="link" url="http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/International/2014/May-09/255880-us-team-arrives-in-nigeria-to-help-with-hostage-search-embassy.ashx"/>
