						<outline text="Just 20% of Dutch voters are interested in EU electionsFriday 09 May 2014"/>
						<outline text="Enthusiasm for the European elections is lacking in the Netherlands, with just 20% of voters saying they are interested in the May 22 vote, according to research by Ipsos."/>
						<outline text="Nevertheless, 82% of people are aware the elections take place later this month, the Ipsos survey found. Turnout at the last EU vote in 2009 was around 40% in the Netherlands."/>
