					<outline text="Russia Plans to Colonize Moon by 2030, Newspaper Reports">
						<outline text="Link to Article" type="link" url="http://www.themoscowtimes.com/news/article/russia-plans-to-colonize-moon-by-2030-newspaper-reports/499806.html"/>
