						<outline text="&quot;I hate to use the words if I were president, so I won't. But what we should have done as soon as we knew these young girls were kidnapped ... we should have utilized every asset that we have, satellite, drones, any capabilities that we had to go after them,&quot; McCain said in an interview with CNN's &quot;The Lead with Jake Tapper.&quot;&quot;We should have mounted a humanitarian mission,&quot; says McCain."/>
